# SUMMARY
Three targeted bug fixes across History, Objects, and Tracking features.
All changes in `navitrack-mobile-apps`. TypeScript clean. One commit.

# DELIVERABLES
- [x] **T1 — History last event:** `useHistoryTimeline.ts` default index changed
      from `0` to `itemsCount - 1`. История tab now highlights the most recent event.
- [x] **T2 — Dual-tank UI:** `VehicleListItem` extended with `fuels: number[]`.
      `vehicleToListItem` populates it from `fuel1`/`fuel2`/`fuel3` when 2+ tanks > 0.
      `ObjectListItem` Row 3 renders individual tank chips for multi-tank vehicles;
      single-tank layout unchanged.
- [x] **T3 — Track arrows zoom:** `PolylineDecorator` spacing formula now derived
      from visible viewport segment length instead of full pixel track length.
      Arrows maintain ~45px density at any zoom level; MAX_ARROWS_COUNT cap preserved.

# VERIFICATION
- pnpm tsc --noEmit → no errors
- Manual test required: History tab, Objects list with multi-tank vehicle, track zoom
